> **Version:** v1.1.0  
> This page documents behavior guaranteed in TealTiger v1.1.0.


# AuditEvent Schema

## Schema version

Audit events use a versioned schema (e.g., `1.0.0`) to allow evolution.

## Required fields

- `schema_version`
- `event_type`
- `timestamp`
- `correlation_id`

## Optional fields

- `trace_id`, `policy_id`, `policy_version`, `mode`, `action`, `reason_codes`, `risk_score`
- `safe_inputs`, `safe_outputs`
- `metadata` (non-sensitive)

## Cost fields

Cost data SHOULD be stored under `metadata.cost.*` (standardized keys).
